---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="CDC → Warehouse - Project">
  <section class="card p-7 reveal">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">CDC → Warehouse</h1>
    <p class="text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-2 py-1 rounded bg-gray-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
      🛠️ In progress - events flowing into incremental models
    </p>

    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
      Change Data Capture from a source database into incremental dbt models. Goal: near-real-time
      “orders today” and a simple customer 360 built on upserts and idempotent loads.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Scope</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300">
      <li>Source Postgres emitting order events (CDC)</li>
      <li>Incremental models with late-arriving data handling</li>
      <li>Latency-aware metrics table for quick reporting</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Status</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300">
      <li>Source schema & event format drafted</li>
      <li><strong>Next:</strong> implement upsert logic and a small live metrics view</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
